    "description": "<strong>STORY</strong><br>What would you do to know, definitively, whether your friends are lying?<br><br>It's Halloween, and for Catherine Seong that means one thing: costumes! But when her best (worst) friend refuses to wear the costume that Cathy had so painstakingly made for her, the only solution is petty revenge. In this case, that means skipping the bar crawl and instead dragging the party into the basement to perform a creepypasta ritual they got off the internet.  After all, what better way to spend an evening with your toxic friend group than summoning a demon who punishes liars?<br><br><strong>ABOUT</strong><br>The Mask Game is a short game about friendship, crushes, communication issues, and demons. <br><br>The ladies from this game will be returning in the upcoming death game .<br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fully voice-acted<br></li><li> 8 endings<br></li><li>Original OST<br></li><li>Illustration gallery<br></li><li>~2 hour playtime</li></ul>",
